            <title>[MAHOUT-1166] Multithreaded version of distributed ALS</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-1166</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Our implementation of ALS broadcasts the feature matrices in each iteration. Therefore, it makes sense to run the mappers in multithreaded mode to not have to load one copy of the feature matrix per core, but share the read-only in-memory copy.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
